io.scanbot.sdk.ui.view.multiple_objects

Class BaseMultipleObjectsDetectorActivity

  • BaseActivity
    • io.scanbot.sdk.ui.view.multiple_objects.BaseMultipleObjectsDetectorActivity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultipleObjectsDetectorActivity

    public class BaseMultipleObjectsDetectorActivity
extends BaseActivity

    Encapsulates all logic for multiple object detection in one RTU component.

    Can be started using Activity.startActivityForResult with Intent from MultipleObjectsDetectorActivity.newIntent - note the requestCode passed.

    Override Activity.onActivityResult and look for noted requestCode.

    Obtain detection result using BaseMultipleObjectsDetectorActivity.parseActivityResult method.

    Also see class MultipleObjectsDetectorConfiguration, RESULT_LICENSE_INVALID

    See Also:
    Activity.startActivityForResult, Intent, MultipleObjectsDetectorActivity.newIntent, Activity.onActivityResult, BaseMultipleObjectsDetectorActivity.parseActivityResult, class MultipleObjectsDetectorConfiguration
